author: asmuts
msg: Adding a rough version of a simple Http Remote Cache Service / Servlet.  It does handle listeners, but it could be used for get, update, and remove in place of the RMI remote cache.  I'll create a basic client framework next.  Eventually we can add in listener registration and UDP discovery, etc.  For now, I'm keeping it very simple.
